    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This driver-focused example is paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include documented subframe reinforcement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and recent rod bearing service to ensure peak reciprocating assembly health. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampening, providing the communicative feedback expected of this platform. This is a high-performance machine optimized for the purist who values mechanical transparency and structural integrity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
