    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic components, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in great shape, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule. We recently completed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, replaced the brake pads, and performed a fresh oil change. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet and comfortable ride. This is a solid, honest car that has been cared for by its previous owner and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
