    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
