      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a reinforced rear subframe to address chassis fatigue and a suspension refreshed with Bilstein dampers for improved lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and light patina, the mechanical synchronization is excellent, having recently undergone a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection. It is a mechanically sound, high-performance icon ready for spirited use.",
